snippet.title: One America News Network
snippet.description: One America News network is a national TV news network airing on Verizon Fios, channel 116. AT&T U-verse, channel 208, and CenturyLink prism, channel 209.  We also stream on Amazon Fire TV, Roku, and Vivicast Media Channel 16. OANN is a new credible source for national and international headlines. An independent, cutting edge platform for political discussions.
